import React from "react";
import {
  GridWrapper,
  ListProduct,
  ProductCard,
  ImageProduct,
  TitleProduct,
  CostProduct
} from "./GridProduct.styles";
import imgproduct1 from "../image/img-01.png";
export default function GridProduct() {
  return (
    <GridWrapper>
      <ListProduct>
        <ProductCard>
          <ImageProduct src={imgproduct1} />
          <TitleProduct>[what happen] How to create</TitleProduct>
          CostProduct
        </ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
        <ProductCard></ProductCard>
      </ListProduct>
    </GridWrapper>
  );
}
